node.text:
She-Hulk Vs Power Girl, remarqued art print. Big Wow Art Facebook group exclusive. 

I know. I know.  I dated myself with that "Tastes Great. Less Filling." joke. 

I've set aside ten art prints for remarques. These ten remarqued art prints are only available for Big Wow Art Facebook group members. (Not a member? Sign up on Facebook.) 

https://www.facebook.com/groups/595571003893680

Steve Morger will sell two remarqued art prints at San Jose Comic Con to Big Wow Art group members only. (He has a list of members. I ain't kidding.) The rest, eight remarques art prints, will be art drop/sold on Big Wow Art on Facebook in the coming weeks. 

Price: $300 each. One per member. 

All proceeds will go to Maui Comic Con and Lake Como Comic Art Fest.

node.text:
Hunchback of Notre Dame, work in progress.

Working on my art commissions for my European art collectors. (See you guys in Lake Como Comic Art Fest in May, guys!) 

https://lccaf.com/

This is my THIRD attempt at the Hunchback. I think I finally got the pose that I'm happy with. The first two didn't have energy. This one feels right in capturing grotesque and twisted form of the Hunchback. 

Now I'm gonna walk away and work on Fight Girls. I'll come back later with fresh eyes and see if the pose still works for me.

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #hunchbackofnotredame #hunchback #universalmonsters #monster #notredame #sanctuary #pencilsketch

CONGRATS TO MY BUDDY ANTHONY MISIANO!!!

My buddy and actor, Anthony Misiano, has a one-man in New York City titled:  I SQUEEZED REALLY HARD

It's produced by Wild Project & The Aviary, and directed by Jacob Titus, running September 17th-26th at Wild Project. 

I'm gonna clear my schedule and go to New York City the weekend of September 25th if anyone wants to watch it with me. Hope to see you guys there.

Use promo code tonysentme you can save $5 off up to 2 tickets!

node.text:
CLASSIC SHE-HULK, omnibus cover.

Had fun channeling John Buscema when I drew this cover. I had to restrain myself and try not to make her too thicc. Looking at it, there's a little bit of Raquel Welch in the figure work. 

I can't wait to see Sabine Rich's color on this.

node.text:
FIGHT GIRLS #5 cover, colored by Sabine Rich.
Cover to issue 5, the FINAL ISSUE!!! Beautifully colored by Sabine Rich. 

Hail to the Queen! Get ready for the shocking high octane conclusion to the Fight Girls storyline. I ain't kidding, you guys are not gonna see this ending coming. It is one twisted ending. I'm still laughing as I'm drawing these last few pages right now. Not for the faint of heart.

Below is the Diamond Distribution Catalogue info to order Fight Girls #5:

Release Date: November 17
Final Order Cutoff: October 25
Diamond Order Code: SEP211342

Thanks, again, everyone for making Fight Girls a smashing success. You guys are the BEST! :-D

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #sabine_rich #fightgirls #hungergames #gladiator #queen @awastudiosofficial @upshotstudiosofficial

node.text:
She-Hulk cover, work in progress. 

Trying to channel John Buscema and draw the classic 1970s She-Hulk. 

Man, the 1970s She-Hulk comics had some crappy forgettable villains. It’s as if they weren’t even trying to make good comics.

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #marvel #shehulk #hulk #gammaray

node.text:
Disney World after MegaCon 2021

My first trip to Disney World ever! After MegaCon, spent Monday with the Torpedo Comics crew in Disney World. We went to the Disney Hollywood and Disney Animal Kingdom. 

The Star Wars rides were fun, but the best damn ride for was the AVATAR ride in Disney's Animal Kingdom. That ride was simply awesome! 

Big thanks to Ashalie, Will, Lo, Lauren, Ben and Ryan for getting me last minute Disney ticket/reservation, and guiding me through the park. You guys are Disney freaks.

@frankchoartist #frankchoartist #torpedocomics #disneyworld #starwars #avatar #florida
